# q035 grandmanager_path
# Intent: Fixed-length sequence path (manager/manager). H8 perf probe: generic path evaluation above unfused scans (see q034; observed 18.75s dims-only on virtual-sf01).
# BI lineage (BI-17): "Who is each employee's manager-of-manager?"
# Predicates verified against enterprise.ttl — DimEmployee: manager (path manager/manager).
PREFIX edw: <http://ns.fluree.dev/edw#>
SELECT ?e ?grandboss
WHERE { ?e a edw:Employee ; edw:manager/edw:manager ?grandboss . }
LIMIT 5000
